Pre-Requisites :

1. Visual Studio 2012 Ultimate edition or Test Agent 2012 & Test Controller 2012 + TCM dependency files GAC'd
2. TFS 2015 and below
3. XAML Definitions to run Test Cases
4. Knowledge on TFS for Testing and MTM
5. Little bit of WIQL (Work Item Query Language)


Description:

This is a wrapper on top of TCM by Microsoft which is used to create, execute and publish test cases to TFS 2015 and below

This solution could be used by developers and qa manual testers to execute automated tests of their choice without requiring to know
MTM and TFS on Testing. Mere knowledge of Test Cases, Test Suites and Build Definitions are sufficient.
